'desc': [u'

Portia Lace Up Knee Length Boots Price: Rs.2399

Bring about a fashionable twist to your look with this pair of uber chic boots! This pair of knee length boots comes with a distressed finish that lends a super fad touch to the overall appeal. A lace that works is way up the front of this pair gives it a fabulous feminine touch. Featuring a side zipper that allows you to slip them on with ease. With flat heels this pair is designed for comfort and style! Wear this pair over skinny jeans and a tucked in loose shirt for a sexy Wild Wild West look!
